ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Ontario Fishery Regulations, 2007
PrecisRegulations Amending the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 2007 in order to (1) update the Regulations to reflect the new filing date for the English and French versions of the maps incorporated by reference in the Regulations; and (2) remove any reference to the Ontario Ministry of Natural Resources' Recreational Fishing Regulations Summary.
